\c 19
\s UElija ubalekela eHorebe
\p
\v 1 UAhabi wasetshela uJezebeli konke uElija ayekwenzile, labo bonke ababulalayo, bonke abaprofethi, ngenkemba\x + 18.40.\x*.
\v 2 Khona uJezebeli wathuma isithunywa kuElija esithi: Kabenze njalo onkulunkulu, bengezelele njalo, uba ngalesisikhathi kusasa ngingenzi impilo yakho ibe njengempilo yomunye wabo\x + Ruthe 1.17.\x*.
\v 3 Ese\add ku\add*bonile, wasukuma, wahamba ngenxa yempilo yakhe, wafika eBherishebha engeyakoJuda\x + Josh. 15.28.\x*, watshiya khona inceku yakhe.
\p
\v 4 Kodwa yena wahamba uhambo losuku enkangala, wafika wahlala ngaphansi kwesihlahla \w serotemu\w**, wacela ukuthi umphefumulo wakhe ufe, wathi: Kwanele, khathesi, N\nd kosi\nd*, thatha impilo yami, ngoba kangingcono kulabobaba\x + Nani 11.15.\x*.
\v 5 Esecambalele elele ngaphansi kwesihlahla esithile serotemu, khangela-ke, khonokho ingilosi yamthinta, yathi kuye: Vuka udle.
\v 6 Wasethalaza, khangela-ke, ekhanda lakhe iqebelengwana losiwe emalahleni, lesigxingi samanzi; wasesidla wanatha, waphinda walala.
\v 7 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasifika ngokwesibili, yamthinta yathi: Vuka udle; ngoba uhambo lwakho lukhulu kakhulu kuwe.
\v 8 Wasevuka wadla wanatha, wahamba ngamandla alokhokudla insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane\x + Eks. 24.18. 34.28. Dute. 9.9,18. Mat. 4.2. Mark. 1.13. Luka 4.2.\x*, waze wafika eHorebe intaba kaNkulunkulu\x + Eks. 3.1.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Wasengena lapho ebhalwini, walala khona ubusuku. Khangela-ke, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuye lathi kuye: Wenzani lapha, Elija?
\v 10 Wathi: Bengitshiseka lokutshisekela iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamabandla\x + Nani 25.11,13. 2 Kho. 10.16.\x*, ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli basitshiyile isivumelwano sakho, badiliza amalathi akho\x + 19.14. 18.30. Roma 11.3.\x*, babulala abaprofethi bakho ngenkemba\x + 18.4.\x*; yimi ngedwa engiseleyo, njalo badinga impilo yami ukuyisusa\x + 18.22.\x*.
\v 11 Wasesithi: Phuma ume entabeni phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*. Khangela-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* yadlula\x + Eks. 24.12. 34.2.\x*. Umoya omkhulu olamandla wasudabula izintaba, waqhekeza amadwala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; \add kodwa\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* yayingekho emoyeni. Lemva komoya ukunyikinyeka komhlaba; \add kodwa\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* yayingekho ekunyikinyekeni komhlaba.
\v 12 Lemva kokunyikinyeka komhlaba umlilo; \add kodwa\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* yayingekho emlilweni\x + Hez. 1.4.\x*. Njalo emva komlilo ilizwi elincinyane elinyenyezayo\x + Jobe 4.16. Hlab. 107.29.\x*.
\v 13 Kwasekuthi uElija e\add li\add*zwa, wathandela ubuso bakhe ngesembatho sakhe, waphuma wema emlonyeni wobhalu\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*. Khangela-ke, leza kuye ilizwi lathi: Wenzani lapha, Elija\x + 19.9.\x*?
\v 14 Wathi: Bengitshisekela lokutshisekela iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamabandla, ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli basitshiyile isivumelwano sakho, badiliza amalathi akho, babulala abaprofethi bakho ngenkemba; yimi ngedwa engiseleyo, njalo badinga impilo yami ukuyisusa\x + 19.10.\x*.
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Hamba, ubuyele ngendlela yakho uye enkangala yeDamaseko\x + 11.24.\x*; lapho usufikile ugcobe uHazayeli abe yinkosi phezu kweSiriya\x + 2 Kho. 8.12,13.\x*,
\v 16 loJehu indodana kaNimshi umgcobe abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 9.1-3.\x*, loElisha indodana kaShafati weAbeli-Mehola umgcobe abe ngumprofethi esikhundleni sakho\x + Hlu. 7.22.\x*.
\v 17 Kuzakuthi-ke ozaphepha enkembeni kaHazayeli\x + 19.15. 2 Kho. 8.8,12. 9.14. 13.3,22,24.\x* uJehu uzambulala\x + 2 Kho. 9.10.\x*, lozaphepha enkembeni kaJehu uElisha uzambulala\x + Hos. 6.5.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa ngitshiyile koIsrayeli abazinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, wonke amadolo angazanga aguqe kuBhali\x + Roma 11.4.\x*, lawo wonke umlomo ongazanga umange\x + Gen. 41.40.\x*.
\s Ubizo lukaElisha
\p
\v 19 Wasesuka lapho, wafica uElisha indodana kaShafati; wayelima ngezipani \add zenkabi\add* zamajogwe alitshumi lambili phambi kwakhe, yena wayelesetshumi lambili. UElija wesesedlula eceleni kwakhe, waphosela isembatho sakhe phezu kwakhe\x + 2 Kho. 2.8.\x*.
\v 20 Wasetshiya izinkabi, wagijima elandela uElija, wathi: Ake ngange ubaba lomama, besengikulandela. Wasesithi kuye: Hamba ubuyele, ngoba ngenzeni kuwe\x + Mat. 8.21,22. Luka 9.61,62.\x*?
\v 21 Wasebuyela ekumlandeleni, wathatha isipani senkabi, wasihlaba, langezikhali zenkabi wapheka inyama yazo, wayinika abantu, bayidla\x + 2 Sam. 24.22.\x*. Wasesuka elandela uElija\x + 2 Kho. 2.1.\x*, wamsebenzela\x + 2 Kho. 6.15.\x*.